b'We want to help our customers in Melbourne metro and Mitchell Shire lockdown postcodes stay in touch with loved ones during this stressful time. From Tuesday 14 July, here\xe2\x80\x99s what we\xe2\x80\x99re doing for them:

:laptop_computer:\xc2\xa0Unlimited data for our eligible consumer and small business home broadband customers \xe2\x80\x93 that\xe2\x80\x99s ADSL, NBN, and cable \xe2\x80\x93 until 31 August 2020.

:mobile_phone:\xc2\xa025GB extra data to use within 30 days is available for our eligible post-paid consumer and small business customers.

:mobile_phone:\xc2\xa0Eligible pre-paid customers who recharge $40+ have an extra 10GB of data available to them for 28 or 30 days from bestowal (depending on their plan).

:telephone_selector: Unlimited standard calls within Australia for eligible pensioner customers on landlines until 31 August 2020. Eligibility is dependent on customer postcode.

Offers available from Tuesday 14 July. Home broadband and landline offers will automatically be added to eligible services.

If you\xe2\x80\x99re a customer in one of these lockdown postcodes, get the mobile data offer via the My Telstra app by applying before 31 August:

1. Head to your service summary page

2. Click the \xe2\x80\x9cExtra data during Covid-19\xe2\x80\x9d link

3. Enter your details

4. The data will be available within 48 hours. You\xe2\x80\x99ll be notified by SMS when it\xe2\x80\x99s applied.

:memo:\xc2\xa0T&Cs

FairPlay Policy applies. Data for use in Australia. Rollover not available. Link in bio for more info.'
